Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:02:02.64,MierukoTV2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs70\pos(1648.762,387.334)}那只怪物到底是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.09,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,真是太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.51,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,太恐怖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.97,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,太瘆人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:04.18,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,仁惠  要是真的做了这种噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:07.19,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,你会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:13.94,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢  那种情况下还是装作没看见比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.65,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,还是说要唱经念佛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.07,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,对对  这个经常有人说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:22.37,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,还有就是撒盐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.29,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,或者用数珠之类的除灵道具？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.25,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,真到危险的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.37,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,就请通灵师来祛除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.91,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,322)\fade(0,222)}华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.91,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(721.334,399.999)\fade(0,222)}小眼眼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.91,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(676,569.333)\fade(0,222)}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.91,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(903.999,637.333)\fade(0,222)}还有，回来时记得买牛奶~
