Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.91,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(774.667,896)\fade(0,222)}不，还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:27.54,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\fade(446,100)\pos(989,302.667)}我在路上了！应该能勉强赶上！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:27.71,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1501.333,519.999)\fade(0,200)}我到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:27.96,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(652,590.666)\fade(446,300)}了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.46,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1473.143,739.428)\fade(278,0)}入手！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.46,MierukoPHONE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678.857,932.571)\fade(278,0)}小眼眼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.88,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,你的对策还真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.30,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,你个人有过什么可怕的经历吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.59,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,浴室堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.22,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,是吗  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.09,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,是姐姐的头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:41.72,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.39,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,话说正在播恐怖节目哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:45.85,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,真的吗  我正想看来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:47.89,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,不过妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.10,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,看来要晚点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.23,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,这不是蜡烛淳二嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.23,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,姐姐对蜡烛淳二没兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.40,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.44,Mieruko up,,0,0,0,,竟然这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.90,Mieruko up,,0,0,0,,请不要找我的内衣哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.65,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,真是  在乱叫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.40,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,什么也没有  赶快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:05.40,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,要走了  回去给你吃饭行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.51,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,见子  要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.22,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,见子  你带雨伞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.02,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.10,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,刚才电视上说今天可能下雨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.44,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,下雨了我就去便利店买一把
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.57,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.57,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,路上小心…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.91,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.75,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,第一节就是数学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.13,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,我记得还有小测  糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.76,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.84,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,早啊  华
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.18,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.72,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,弹力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.39,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,不过你的惊吓反应有点淡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:19.69,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,这才早上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.98,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,是小眼眼  你已经买啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.61,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,对  在杂货书店买的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.95,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,真好啊  我也想要一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.82,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,那里也有华喜欢的小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:33.70,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,是拉姆兔  拉姆达小兔兔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.20,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.54,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,拉姆兔在店里有很多限定产品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.54,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,很快就会一售而空的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:44.88,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,即使如此  你房间里也全是它的玩偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.01,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:47.05,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,别挡道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.30,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:58.68,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.37,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.12,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.91,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,隔壁班的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.42,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:29.63,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,这里重点要思考主人公为什么变成了老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.34,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,其实不太明白对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.68,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,也对啊  大家对此怎么看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.31,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,要是自己变成了老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.06,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,逐渐忘记自己曾是人类之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.65,Mieruko,,0,0,0,,四谷同学！
